---
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-potrero-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  {/* Líneas decorativas de campo (topo-lines) */}
  <svg
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-[0.08]"
    viewBox="0 0 800 400"
    preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
  >
    {Array.from({ length: 10 }).map((_, i) => (
      <path
        d={`M-80,${40 + i * 40} C150,${20 + i * 40} 350,${70 + i * 40} 500,${30 + i * 40} S800,${10 + i * 40} 900,${50 + i * 40}`}
        fill="none"
        stroke="#E8DCC4"
        stroke-width="0.8"
      />
    ))}
  </svg>

  <div class="container-prose relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-earth-400 text-xs md:text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-3">
        La solución
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.5rem] mb-8">
        Sabé <em class="italic text-earth-400">exactamente</em><br />
        cuánto te sale cada kilo.
      </h2>

      {/* KPI estrella visual */}
      <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-3 bg-potrero-800/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl px-10 py-8 border border-earth-400/20 mb-10">
        <span class="eyebrow !text-earth-400">Costo por kilo producido</span>
        <p class="font-display font-medium text-earth-400 tabular-nums leading-none"
           style="font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);">
          $ 1.85<span class="text-3xl text-earth-300/70 ml-1">/kg</span>
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-2 text-sm text-earth-200/70">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-earth-400"></span>
            Directos: $1.12
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-earth-300"></span>
            Indirectos: $0.73
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-earth-200/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Potrero agarra todos tus gastos, los cruza con la carne que produjiste, y te dice
        <span class="text-earth-300 font-semibold">en una pantalla</span>
        qué tan rentable es tu campo. Sin Excel. Sin asesor. Sin esperar fin de año.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
